Adaptive Fighting				CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat			PREABILITY:3,CATEGORY=FEAT,TYPE=Combat																																																																																																																																			DESC:You can adjust your fighting style to match specific conditions during combat.									STACK:NO	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:NUMCHOICES=3|ABILITYSELECTION|FEAT|!PC,QUALIFIED[TYPE=Combat]								SELECT:3																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.154																																														BENEFIT:Select three combat feats that you do not have but whose prerequisites you meet. Once per day as a move action, you can gain the benefit of one of these feats for 1 minute. Each time you gain a level, you can replace one of these three selected feats with a different feat that you don't have but meet the prerequisites for.
