Improved Combat Maneuver		CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat																																																																																																																		PRETOTALAB:1																								DESC:You are particularly skilled with a specific combat maneuver.											STACK:YES	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:NOCHOICE																																																																																																																																																																																				BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Improved Combat Maneuver Selection|1																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.158																																														BENEFIT:Choose one combat maneuver (bull rush, dirty trick, disarm, grapple, reposition, sunder, or trip). You gain a +4 bonus to your attack roll to resolve that combat maneuver.&nl;Special: You can take Improved Combat Maneuver multiple times. The effects don't stack. Each time you take the feat, it applies to a new combat maneuver.
