Improved Great Fortitude		CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:General		PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Great Fortitude																				PREMULT:1,[PRELEVEL:MIN=5],[PREVARGTEQ:EffectiveLVL,5]																																																																																																					DESC:You are more resistant to diseases, poisons, and dangers.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.158																																														BENEFIT:You can spend 1 RP to reroll a failed Fortitude save (see page 243).
